OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy and breezy for most,
OL,6,Fwith spells of rain affecting many
OL,7,Fplaces. Heavier and more persistent
OL,8,Foutbreaks of rain likely across
OL,9,Fwestern hills. Temperatures around or
OL,10,Fslightly above normal.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FRemaining cloudy overnight
OL,13,Fwith rain spreading eastwards. The
OL,14,Frain over western hills more likely to
OL,15,Fbe heavier, with hill fog. Breezy
OL,16,Fwinds continue.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
