OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FMonday, cloudy with spells of
OL,6,Frain at times, mostly affecting
OL,7,Fwestern hills with drier conditions
OL,8,Ffurther east and sunny intervals along
OL,9,Fthe coast. Temperatures becoming warm.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:
OL,12,FTuesday, cloudy with spells of rain at
OL,13,Ftimes, mostly affecting western hills
OL,14,Fwith drier conditions further east.
OL,15,FWednesday and Thursday becoming drier
OL,16,Fand sunnier. Temperatures becoming
OL,17,Frather warm.
